Day 29 - 680*
It was really good, the art enjoyable, the hentai unnecessary but pretty good and the story fantastic with exception of a few plot points that I did not like.
Overall, 7/10.

This is pretty great read. If you look at a Hdoujin perspective, this is pretty terrible but if you read this in a manga perspective, this is a great one. A hidden gem indeed. 10/10, didn't regret reading this.
